org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor

Class ReverseBundleProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor.ForwardingBundleProcessor
      • org.apache.felix.ipojo.extender.internal.processor.ReverseBundleProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BundleProcessor, Lifecycle

    public class ReverseBundleProcessor
extends ForwardingBundleProcessor
    A bundle processor delegating a wrapped bundle processor. On stop, the bundles are processed in reverse.
